cast.overview: As Agnes slowly dies of cancer, her sisters are so immersed in their own psychic pains that they are unable to offer her the support she needs.
cast.title: Cries and Whispers

details.biography: Ingrid Bergman, born Karlebo, was a Swedish film crew member, had a BA, and was the fifth wife of Ingmar Bergman. Ingrid Bergman was born on January 17, 1930 in Stockholm, Stockholms län, Sweden as Ingrid Karlebo. She is known for her work on Fanny e Alexander (1982), Sonata de Outono (1978) and Da Vida das Marionetes (1980). She was married to Ingmar Bergman and Jan-Carl von Rosen. She died on May 20, 1995.
details.name: Ingrid Bergman
